[[File:Mitani_Shrine.png|thumb]] 

{{ill|Mitanino Shrine|WD=Q135038741}} is a shrine in the Engishiki.<ref>https://jun-yu-roku.com/yamashiro-otokuni-jododani-mitani/</ref> This shrine is not very well known historically. Possibly linked to the nearby temple Jogan-ji 乗願寺<ref>https://kyonoreijo.sakura.ne.jp/rakusaik/rsk91.htm</ref>.<ref>https://youtu.be/_829_Fz2mLc</ref>

== Gods ==

* '''[[:ja:天児屋根命|天児屋根命]]'''
* '''[[:ja:応神天皇|応神天皇]]'''
* '''[[:ja:別雷神|別雷神]]'''
* '''[[:ja:倉稲魂神|倉稲魂神]]'''

